title: AgentSet.ai vs Haystack Methodologies
body_html:
Comparison of AgentSet.ai and Haystack

Methodologies

  • AgentSet.ai: Platform for building, deploying, and managing AI agents.
  • Haystack: Web application by Deepset, deploying Haystack pipelines as REST APIs.

Tests Conducted

  • Embedding functions
  • Dynamic tool pruning
  • Integration workflows

Observations

  • Performance differences
  • Integration ease and flexibility

Conclusion

  • Recommendations based on specific use-cases and requirements.
